---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Contact Angel Bail Bonds"
  description="Contact Angel Bail Bonds in Stillwater, Oklahoma. Phone: (405) 614-3000. Available 24/7 for emergency bail bond services."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-deep) 0%, var(--navy) 100%); padding: 80px 1.5rem 56px;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 style="color: white; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Contact Us</h1>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto;">
        Get in touch with Angel Bail Bonds. Available 24/7 for emergencies.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--slate-50);">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <div>
          <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Get In Touch</h2>

          <!-- Phone -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-agate text-xl mb-2">Phone</h3>
            <a 
              href="tel:+14056143000" 
              class="text-gold text-2xl font-bold hover:text-agate transition-colors"
            >
              (405) 614-3000
            </a>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-2">Available 24/7 for emergencies</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Email -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-agate text-xl mb-2">Email</h3>
            <a 
              href="mailto:bailbondangel@gmail.com" 
              class="text-gold hover:text-agate transition-colors"
            >
              bailbondangel@gmail.com
            </a>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-2">We'll respond as soon as possible</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Location -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-agate text-xl mb-2">Location</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-2">
              <strong>Stillwater, Oklahoma</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
              Serving Payne, Pawnee, Lincoln, Kay & Noble Counties
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Hours -->
          <div class="mb-8 bg-gold/10 border-2 border-gold/30 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-agate text-xl mb-4">Hours</h3>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
              <p><strong>Monday - Friday:</strong> 24/7 Available</p>
              <p><strong>Saturday - Sunday:</strong> 24/7 Available</p>
              <p><strong>Holidays:</strong> 24/7 Available</p>
              <p class="text-gold font-semibold mt-3">Always Ready for Emergencies</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Links -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate text-xl mb-4">Quick Links</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>
                <a href="/services" class="text-agate hover:text-gold transition-colors font-semibold">
                  View Services →
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/how-bail-works" class="text-agate hover:text-gold transition-colors font-semibold">
                  How Bail Works →
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/about" class="text-agate hover:text-gold transition-colors font-semibold">
                  About Karri →
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/" class="text-agate hover:text-gold transition-colors font-semibold">
                  Back to Home →
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div>
          <div class="card bg-white">
            <h3 class="text-agate text-2xl mb-6">Send Us a Message</h3>

            <form action="/api/contact" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
              <!-- Name -->
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="block text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">
                  Your Name
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  id="name" 
                  name="name" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-charcoal/20 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-agate transition-colors"
                  placeholder="John Doe"
                />
              </div>

              <!-- Email -->
              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">
                  Email Address
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="email" 
                  id="email" 
                  name="email" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-charcoal/20 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-agate transition-colors"
                  placeholder="john@example.com"
                />
              </div>

              <!-- Phone -->
              <div>
                <label for="phone" class="block text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">
                  Phone Number
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="tel" 
                  id="phone" 
                  name="phone" 
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-charcoal/20 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-agate transition-colors"
                  placeholder="(405) 555-0000"
                />
              </div>

              <!-- Subject -->
              <div>
                <label for="subject" class="block text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">
                  Subject
                </label>
                <select 
                  id="subject" 
                  name="subject" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-charcoal/20 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-agate transition-colors"
                >
                  <option value="">Select a subject</option>
                  <option value="emergency">Emergency Bail Bond Needed</option>
                  <option value="question">General Question</option>
                  <option value="service">Service Information</option>
                  <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <!-- Message -->
              <div>
                <label for="message" class="block text-charcoal font-semibold mb-2">
                  Message
                </label>
                <textarea 
                  id="message" 
                  name="message" 
                  rows="5"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-charcoal/20 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-agate transition-colors resize-none"
                  placeholder="Tell us how we can help..."
                ></textarea>
              </div>

              <!-- Submit Button -->
              <button 
                type="submit"
                class="w-full btn-primary"
              >
                Send Message
              </button>
            </form>

            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-gold/10 border-l-4 border-gold rounded">
              <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">
                <strong>For emergencies:</strong> Call us immediately at <a href="tel:+14056143000" class="text-gold font-bold">(405) 614-3000</a>. This form is for general inquiries.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->

  <!-- Service Areas Map -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-agate text-3xl mb-8 text-center">Service Areas</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Map Placeholder -->
        <div class="bg-agate/5 border-2 border-agate/20 rounded-lg h-96 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 mb-4">Service Map</p>
            <p class="text-2xl text-gold">5 Central Oklahoma Counties</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Counties List -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate text-2xl mb-6">We Serve:</h3>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-cream rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">📍</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-agate">Payne County</h4>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">Including Stillwater • Primary Service Area</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-cream rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">📍</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-agate">Pawnee County</h4>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">Central Oklahoma Coverage</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-cream rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">📍</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-agate">Lincoln County</h4>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">South Service Territory</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-cream rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">📍</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-agate">Kay County</h4>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">North Coverage Area</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-cream rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">📍</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-agate">Noble County</h4>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-sm">East Territory</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 bg-agate/10 border-2 border-agate/20 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              <strong>Not in our service area?</strong> Contact us anyway. We may be able to help or refer you to a trusted partner.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--slate-50);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-agate text-3xl mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="card bg-white group cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold text-agate">
            <span>What is a bail bond?</span>
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-4 pt-4 border-t">
            A bail bond is a contract where we (Angel Bail Bonds) agree to pay the full bail amount to the court if you fail to appear at your court date. You pay us a non-refundable premium (typically 10% of the bail amount) instead of paying the full bail to the court.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="card bg-white group cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold text-agate">
            <span>How quickly can you get someone out of jail?</span>
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-4 pt-4 border-t">
            In most cases, we can have someone released within 1-2 hours of posting the bail bond. The exact time depends on the jail's processing time. Call us immediately when bail is set and we'll work as fast as possible.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="card bg-white group cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold text-agate">
            <span>Do you offer payment plans?</span>
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-4 pt-4 border-t">
            Yes! We understand that bail can be a financial burden. We work with most clients to create flexible payment plans that fit their budget. Call us to discuss your options.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="card bg-white group cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold text-agate">
            <span>What do I need to get a bail bond?</span>
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-4 pt-4 border-t">
            You'll need: (1) The inmate's name and booking number, (2) The jail location, (3) The bail amount set by the judge, (4) Proof of income or ability to pay the premium, and (5) A valid photo ID.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="card bg-white group cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold text-agate">
            <span>What happens if they miss court?</span>
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-4 pt-4 border-t">
            If the defendant fails to appear, you (or the co-signer) become liable for the full bail amount. A warrant will be issued and we may contact you to help locate them. This is why choosing a responsible co-signer is critical.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="card bg-white group cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold text-agate">
            <span>Are you available 24/7?</span>
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mt-4 pt-4 border-t">
            Yes! We're available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. Arrests don't happen on a schedule, and neither do we take time off. Call (405) 614-3000 anytime.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding text-white" style="background: var(--navy-deep);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6">Need Immediate Help?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8">
        Don't wait. Call Angel Bail Bonds now for 24/7 emergency bail bond services.
      </p>

      <a 
        href="tel:+14056143000" 
        class="btn-primary"
      >
        (405) 614-3000
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
